headline.print_headline: South African Leads in Home Event
headline.main: South African Leads in Home Event

snippet: Jaco van Zyl shot a seven-under-par 65 to top a South African-dominated leaderboard in the first round of the South African Open in Gauteng, in the European Tour’s first event of 2016.
lead_paragraph: Jaco van Zyl shot a seven-under-par 65 to top a South African-dominated leaderboard in the first round of the South African Open in Gauteng, in the European Tour’s first event of 2016.
